Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.51,0:01:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和这个人一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.57,0:01:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.11,0:01:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向姐姐炫耀你们感情融洽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.16,0:01:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不觉得羞耻吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就没有一点罪恶感吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.70,0:02:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐现在需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.29,0:02:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想你陪在她身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而你却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.97,0:02:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.42,0:02:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥恢复了意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶…是不是小了点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什么  速濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种成绩连初中生都不如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.96,0:02:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这三年你都为了什么在练习？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就满足了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.34,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想夺冠后进职业队的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.23,0:03:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要以为这种成绩就能混进职业队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样是在拖别人的后腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有斗志的家伙就给我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  又没锁门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.53,0:04:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.33,0:04:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不晒晒太阳的话会发霉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早饭还没吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我买了便当 要吃完哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我回公司了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.67,0:04:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出门的时候要把门锁好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.84,0:04:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 已经这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要挨骂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟 速濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.74,0:04:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干吗慌慌张张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二  来的正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好我午休结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 再快些 拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不认真工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心被炒鱿鱼哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二才是呢 这种时候在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当心考试不及格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速濑  你又去了孝之那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该放手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已经一年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直依赖于你的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.99,0:05:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迟迟不肯振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候放手不管反而会更好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙也已经是大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.12,0:05:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 凉宫的事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是速濑的错呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.99,0:05:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 多亏你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.26,0:05:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二可要再勉强自己多学一些哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天做什么菜好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  习惯学校生活了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  已经完全没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.73,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为新人种子选手\N游泳部那边的成绩也飞快上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 游泳部的大家还好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…有点失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他们是那么过分的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得理想破灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  虽然他们有的地方会很严厉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但都不是坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.09,0:06:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说前辈的坏话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.14,0:07:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说前辈进不了职业队是因为迷恋男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.83,0:07:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.06,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们明明不了解对真相…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 水月前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏有你照顾哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…没什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.68,0:07:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己要这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的朋友嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能不管吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他一个人住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有些不方便的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.73,0:07:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后也要请你多多照看哥哥和姐姐的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.96,0:07:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐一定会醒过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.73,0:07:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你件事可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.44,0:08:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拍了在游泳部练习时的录像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话帮我看看我的动作之类好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己会看不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道是不是帮得到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.48,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.72,0:08:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明叫他出去要锁门的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太不小心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.46,0:09:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该换了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速濑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去把汤热一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天出去玩玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是星期天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.11,0:10:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且偶尔也该出去走走...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.14,0:10:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 孝之 看呀看呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.81,0:10:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一个水槽里放进\N这么多种类的鱼没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大的不会吃了小的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.19,0:10:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难得出来一趟  高兴一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速濑 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速濑 喂 别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生气了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看呀看呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得这两个很可爱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都给你做饭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.20,0:11:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没你办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.63,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我这两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.48,0:11:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.26,0:12:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔出来走走也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 去喝茶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我再逛逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想买点书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.00,0:12:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样呀 之后电话联络吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.42,0:12:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要开连环画展了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.78,0:13:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是鸣海 我现在不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.81,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事的话请在听到提示音后留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.32,0:13:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有回来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才买的马克杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是放在你那里好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我现在过来  拜托你咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没 没来我这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想…没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.73,0:13:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分开的时候还很精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.33,0:13:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是孝之没有手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你担心过头了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果联络上我会告诉你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来的话跟我联系 -水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.57,0:14:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥 连环画展又要开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
