Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  很想去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  天已经很晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.94,0:15:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再错过就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.65,0:15:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  既然遥那么说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.15,0:15:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天鸣海君没有来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探望时间已经过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来也要明天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很急吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.60,0:15:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行呀  擅自把患者带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少挡我路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥说过她想去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去的话 不快点去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连环画展就结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.86,0:15:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约好了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.11,0:15:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和遥约好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.73,0:15:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算去了她也看不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是最清楚的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直呆在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 孝之也很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.18,0:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.31,0:16:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.69,0:16:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.86,0:17:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很了解你是多么地重视遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.91,0:17:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而 说实话看到你这样我们很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
