Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.67,0:17:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 鸣海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.75,0:17:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再来探望我女儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
